      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks. so like, when you say \"tense competition\" or \"mistrust,\" are we talking about actual violence? i've heard some stuff about certain groups being more \"warlike\" or aggressive than others because of their history. is there a specific group that tends to be the primary driver of the instability?",
